window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The race has ended. The new prize is survival.</p> <p>In the aftermath of the thwarted alien invasion, Arlo teams up with his old nemesis to seek a potential ally. With the creation of FTL outfitted Racers, they’re finally able to cross great distances in a short period of time.</p> <p>What they find at Refuge is shocking. Aided by their new friends, Arlo must fight his way home, bringing information vital to Earth’s continued existence.</p> <p>At least now it’s two against one.</p> <p>The space battle is on.</p> <p>From the author of <i>The Survivors</i> and <i>Baldwin's Legacy</i> comes the stunning sequel to <i>Space Race</i>.</p>"; 
